AdminAccountController
- POST    /api/admins                     → createAdmin
- DELETE  /api/admins/{id}               → deleteAdmin
- PUT     /api/admins/{id}/name          → updateAdminName
- PUT     /api/admins/{id}/email         → updateAdminEmail
- GET     /api/admins/{id}               → getAdminById

TeamMemberAccountController
- POST    /api/members                   → createTeamMember
- DELETE  /api/members/{id}             → deleteTeamMember
- PUT     /api/members/{id}/name        → updateTeamMemberName
- PUT     /api/members/{id}/email       → updateTeamMemberEmail
- GET     /api/members/{id}             → getTeamMemberById

AdminController
- POST    /api/admins/actions/assign-team         → assignToTeam
- PUT     /api/admins/actions/{id}/role           → changeRole
- PATCH   /api/admins/actions/tasks/{id}/lock     → lockTask
- PATCH   /api/admins/actions/tasks/{id}/unlock   → unlockTask
- GET     /api/admins                             → getAdmins
- PUT     /api/admins/actions/{id}/reset      → resetPassword

AuthInfoController
- POST    /api/auth/login               → login
- GET     /api/auth/{id}/admin          → isAdmin

TeamMemberController
- PUT     /api/members/actions/{id}/password   → changePassword
- GET     /api/members/{id}/teams              → getTeamsForMember
- GET     /api/members/{id}/tasks              → getAssignedTasks
- GET     /api/members                         → getTeamMembers

TaskController
- POST    /api/tasks                   → createTask
- DELETE  /api/tasks/{id}             → deleteTask
- PUT     /api/tasks/{id}             → editTask

TeamController
- POST    /api/teams                   → createTeam
- DELETE  /api/teams/{id}             → deleteTeam
- PUT     /api/teams/{id}/lead        → changeTeamLead
- GET     /api/teams                  → getAllTeams

NotificationController
- GET     /api/notifications/unread/{id}    → getUnreadNotifications
- GET     /api/notifications/read/{id}      → getReadNotifications
- PUT     /api/notifications/{id}/read      → markAsRead
- PUT     /api/notifications/{id}/unread    → markAsUnread
- DELETE  /api/notifications/{id}           → deleteNotification

IsMemberOfController
- POST    /api/memberships                             → addMemberToTeam
- DELETE  /api/memberships/{teamId}/{memberId}         → removeMemberFromTeam
- GET     /api/memberships/{teamId}/{memberId}         → isMemberOfTeam

IsAssignedController
- POST    /api/assignments                             → assignToTask
- DELETE  /api/assignments/{taskId}/{memberId}         → unassignFromTask
- GET     /api/assignments/{taskId}/{memberId}         → isAssignedToTask

Notes:
AuthController route mapping changed from /auth-info to /api/auth
Notification route mapping changed from /notif to /api/notifications